examples.text: Sen de olmazsan eğer, batar artık bu gemi.
examples.translation: Now if you too aren't here, this ship will sink.

glosses: to set; Of a heavenly body, to disappear below the horizon of a planet, etc, as it rotates.
to be stuck, to be pierced (pressed into with a sharp point.)
to fall, collapse; to be overthrown or defeated.

etymology: From Ottoman Turkish باتمق (batmak), from Proto-Turkic *bat-. Compare Old Turkic [script needed] (bat-).
